  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">If one solution to the system of equations above is <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the ordered pair x comma y \"></span>, what is one possible value of <span class=\"italic\">x</span> ?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [],
  "keys": [],
  "rationale": "<p>The correct answer is either 8 or 9. The first equation can be rewritten as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"y equals, 17 minus x\"></span>. Substituting <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"17 minus x\"></span> for <span class=\"italic\">y</span> in the second equation gives <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x times, open parenthesis, 17 minus x, close parenthesis, equals 72\"></span>. By applying the distributive property, this can be rewritten as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"17 x, minus x squared, equals 72\"></span>. Subtracting 72 from both sides of the equation yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x squared, minus 17 x, plus 72, equals 0\"></span>. Factoring the left-hand side of this equation yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, x minus 8, close parenthesis, times, open parenthesis, x minus 9, close parenthesis, equals 0\"></span>. Applying the Zero Product Property, it follows that <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x minus 8, equals 0\"></span> and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x minus 9, equals 0\"></span>. Solving each equation for <span class=\"italic\">x</span> yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals 8\"></span> and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals 9\"></span> respectively. Note that 8 and 9 are examples of ways to enter a correct answer.</p>\n",
